<div class="heading resPageHeading">


























<h1 >Accessibility & Accommodation</h1></div>

<div class="content stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resTabs section">
























 



<div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12">
        <!-- Tabs Component -->
        <div class="tabs">
            <!-- Nav tabs -->
            <ul class="nav nav-tabs nav-tabs-responsive" role="tablist">
                
                <li role="presentation" class="active">
                    <a id="tab-1601398701770-accessibility-accommodation-requests" href="#tab-content-1601398701770-accessibility-accommodation-requests" role="tab" data-toggle="tab" aria-controls="tab-content-1601398701770-accessibility-accommodation-requests" aria-expanded="true">
                        <span class="text">Accessibility Accommodation Requests</span>
                    </a>
                </li>
                
                <li role="presentation" class="next">
                    <a id="tab-1601398703881-accommodations-at-ryerson" href="#tab-content-1601398703881-accommodations-at-ryerson" role="tab" data-toggle="tab" aria-controls="tab-content-1601398703881-accommodations-at-ryerson" aria-expanded="false">
                        <span class="text">Accommodations at Ryerson</span>
                    </a>
                </li>
                
            </ul>
            <!-- Tab panes -->
            <div class="tab-content">
                
                <div tabindex="0" id="tab-content-1601398701770-accessibility-accommodation-requests" role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane container-clipboard fade in active" aria-labelledby="tab-1601398701770-accessibility-accommodation-requests">
                    <div class="1601398701770 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="335829b3-38e5-4295-89cc-2595c01660be" >

    <p>Ryerson Housing &amp; Residence Life understands that students living in residence may require accessibility accommodations for a variety of reasons. Meeting our students accommodation and accessibility needs are important to us. Please read the following information to better understand what may qualify as an accommodation and how to apply for an accommodation request when applying to live in residence.</p> 
<p>If a student has any <strong>medical, dietary, disability or religious needs that may require specific accommodations in residence,</strong> they must indicate “Yes” on the housing application.</p> 
<p>Completing a Residence Accessibility Accommodation Request form allows us to have a clearer picture of a student’s needs as it pertains to living in residence. <strong>Please note that submission of a Residence Accessibility Accommodation Request form does not guarantee a spot in residence.</strong> Submitting a completed Accessibility Accommodation Request allows Housing &amp; Residence Life to determine what room-style and accommodations an applicant may receive once offered a space. While we strive to accommodate residents’ needs, we cannot guarantee a specific room-style.</p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#335829b3-38e5-4295-89cc-2595c01660be");});</script></div>

				</div>

                    
                </div>
                
                <div tabindex="0" id="tab-content-1601398703881-accommodations-at-ryerson" role="tabpanel" class="tab-pane container-clipboard fade" aria-labelledby="tab-1601398703881-accommodations-at-ryerson">
                    <div class="1601398703881 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="69a615ab-cca5-4baa-ad7f-2b71f1d34afe" >

    <p>Please note that the Residence Accessibility Accommodations Request Form is valid only for accommodations in residence.</p> 
<p><img src="/etc.clientlibs/ryecms/static/clientlib-site/resources/images/separators/transparent_separator.png" alt=" " role="presentation" class="hr-separator hr-separator-default">&nbsp;</p> 
<h2>Meal Plan Accommodations</h2> 
<p>Indicating a need for dietary accommodation will only affect whether an applicant may be placed in a space with kitchen facilities. Meal plans are mandatory for all students living in residence. If a student requires an accommodation for the mandatory meal plan, they will need to connect specifically with <a href="https://www.ryerson.ca/university-business-services/food/">Ryerson Food Services</a>.</p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#69a615ab-cca5-4baa-ad7f-2b71f1d34afe");});</script></div>

				</div>

                    
                </div>
                
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>



</div>

				

				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="ae9c940c-1234-4e1c-ba8b-ef8257ee0bf9" >

    <h2><strong>How to Submit an Accessibility Accommodation Request</strong></h2>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#ae9c940c-1234-4e1c-ba8b-ef8257ee0bf9");});</script></div>

				

				
				<div class="resAccordion section">
























 


<div class="row">
    <div class="col-xs-12">
        <div class="panel-group accordion background-hidden" id="8793fd9b-4315-4e58-90fc-0b0a9d7a34c4" role="tablist" aria-multiselectable="true">
			
            
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <!-- Accordion Heading -->
                <div class="panel-heading container-clipboard">
                    <h3 class="panel-title">
                        <a id="accordion-1601398834342-step-1--complete-a-residence-application" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#8793fd9b-4315-4e58-90fc-0b0a9d7a34c4" href="#accordion-content-1601398834342-step-1--complete-a-residence-application" aria-controls="accordion-content-1601398834342-step-1--complete-a-residence-application" aria-expanded="false">
                            Step 1: Complete a Residence Application
                        </a>
                    </h3>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1601398834342-step-1--complete-a-residence-application" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1601398834342-step-1--complete-a-residence-application">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1601398834342 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="0f536fb2-3b4d-4227-b134-335025c738df" >

    <p>Complete a Residence Application by the application <strong>deadline, June 1, 2020</strong> to be considered in the 2020-2021 <a href="/content/ryerson/housing/future-students/applying.html">1st Round of Residence Offers</a>. When prompted, select “Yes” to requiring an accessibility accommodation. Be sure to complete the Emergency Evacuation section.</p>
    





</div>
<script>$(document).ready(function(){addCoursePopover("#0f536fb2-3b4d-4227-b134-335025c738df");});</script></div>

