                    <h3 class="panel-title">
                        <a id="accordion-1599072448215-what-is-a--qualifying-professional--" role="tab" data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#e40eab0c-90a7-4fd4-bef1-61ab82bb6833" href="#accordion-content-1599072448215-what-is-a--qualifying-professional--" aria-controls="accordion-content-1599072448215-what-is-a--qualifying-professional--" aria-expanded="false">
                            What is a “qualifying professional”?
                        </a>
                    </h3>
                    
                </div>
                <!-- Accordion Body -->
                <div tabindex="0" id="accordion-content-1599072448215-what-is-a--qualifying-professional--" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="accordion-1599072448215-what-is-a--qualifying-professional--">
                    <div class="panel-body ">
                        <div class="1599072448215 stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resText parbase section">


























<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="7014c9c8-d5d0-47b7-ac95-27a538406e2c" >

    <p>A qualifying professional may be a healthcare practitioner (medical doctor, psychologist, psychiatrist etc.) or a recognized religious leader. They should be able to attest to the applicant’s need(s) and assess their impact on their ability to successfully live in residence.</p> 
<p>If there are any questions about whether a qualifying professional is appropriate, please contact Housing &amp; Residence Life by phone (416)-979-5284 or email at <a href="mailto:housing@ryerson.ca" target="_blank">housing@ryerson.ca<span aria-hidden="true" class="autoIconLink fa fa-external-link"></span><span class="sr-only">, opens in new window</span></a>.<br> </p>
    





</div>
